 * Add `a + b` as `u32`, erroring instead of wrapping on overflow.
 *
 * @param a  the augend
 * @param b  the addend
 * @return      `a + b` as `u32`, or an `error` if the sum exceeds `u32::MAX`
 * @throws      when `a > u32::MAX - b`
